{"tid":1415184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日 升級定唔升級！！佔 領 機 場 ?","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:06:02.000Z","uid":257736,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"813d4fcab5ab0aa3134a4f5c6cfd36d1b107d2f4","tid":1415184,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:20:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_7750000/newsid_7757700/7757787.stm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2Fchinese%2Ftrad%2Fhi%2Fnewsid_7750000%2Fnewsid_7757700%2F7757787.stm&d=m%2FvCTr80Ma3Q2SiS6jp77btp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=b951a665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_7750000/newsid_7757700/7757787.stm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />升級，正皮，佔領機場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔升級，負皮<br />\n<br />\n目前仍有十萬名遊客被困在曼谷。雖然有關方面正在採取措施，使用其他機場疏散，但是，BBC在曼谷的記者夏昆汀說，對於很多人來說，立刻就能回家的希望仍然非常渺茫。<br />\n<br />\n他說，在機場內，示威者打好床鋪，做好了繼續堅守的準備。他們有充足的食物和飲用水。<br />\n<br />\n機場內，電視上和廣播中仍然不斷傳出示威組織者的演講，要求泰國總理頌猜下台。<br />\n<br />\n頌猜說，他不會辭職，但是他又未能驅散示威者。泰國陸軍不支持頌猜，警方的努力迄今成效不大，危機仍在繼續。"},{"pid":"8a56c9b7a3e40c5a64ccc2bc0ffe93ff66a706af","tid":1415184,"uid":260783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"估佢老母臭系啦，記住帶防具。<br />\n仲有機場唔建議魔法。"},{"pid":"90c0cc7899cb4e4574103c11ac1ba84e6d9145d8","tid":1415184,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82dc76aaf65b4274b497cabd765b28c6d8e93192","tid":1415184,"uid":182575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"直擊心臟"},{"pid":"b5bc10a9a871b97da1247f3415df2a3f8aff18f7","tid":1415184,"uid":39568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:06:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong>推晒所有機場post<br />\n機場好重要<br />\n絕對係一個大既國際新聞<br />\n8月9-11日<br />\n和理非進場<br />\n唔好比港共轉移視線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFeQsAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFeQsAz.jpg&h=ead62688&s={SIZE}\" /></strong></strong></span>"}]}